		<abstract id="abstract">
			<title>Eclipse RAP Tutorial</title>
			<para> This tutorial describes how to create
				Eclipse RAP
				applications and how to use the CSS theming to modify their look.
				Eclipse RAP aims to enable developers to build
				rich,
				Ajax-enabled web
				applications by using the Eclipse development
				model. </para>
			<para>  This tutorial is based on Eclipse 3.7 (Indigo).
			</para>
		</abstract>
